---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<h1>üöÄ Hey there, I'm Arthur Dell!</h1>
				<div class="tagline">
					<p><strong>I AM ARTHUR DELL - ON DEMAND! üí™</strong></p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="intro">
				<p>
					Welcome to my corner of the internet! I'm not your average guy - I live life at full throttle 
					and I'm always ready for the next adventure. Whether I'm gliding through the city on my 
					rollerblades, scaling walls with parkour moves, or discovering the most incredible food spots, 
					I bring passion and excitement to everything I do.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Life's too short to be boring, right? That's why I've made it my mission to squeeze every 
					drop of excitement out of every single day. From sunrise workouts to midnight food runs, 
					I'm <em>always</em> ON DEMAND!
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="highlights">
				<h2>What Gets Me Excited? üåü</h2>
				<div class="grid">
					<div class="card">
						<h3>üõº Rollerblading</h3>
						<p>The wind in my hair, the rhythm of the wheels - there's nothing like carving through the streets with style!</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card">
						<h3>üèÉ‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Parkour</h3>
						<p>Why walk around obstacles when you can go over, under, and through them? The city is my playground!</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card">
						<h3>üçï Food Adventures</h3>
						<p>From hole-in-the-wall tacos to five-star dining experiences - I'm on a mission to taste it all!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta">
				<p>
					Ready to learn more about my wild adventures and epic food discoveries? 
					Check out my <a href="/about">About page</a> for the full stories!
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
		
		<style>
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 2em 0;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
				color: white;
				margin: -1em -1em 2em -1em;
			}
			
			.hero h1 {
				font-size: 2.5em;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			
			.tagline {
				font-size: 1.3em;
				background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
				padding: 1em;
				border-radius: 10px;
				display: inline-block;
			}
			
			.intro {
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto 3em auto;
				font-size: 1.1em;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			
			.highlights {
				margin: 3em 0;
			}
			
			.highlights h2 {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 2em;
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
				color: #667eea;
			}
			
			.grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5em;
				margin-bottom: 3em;
			}
			
			.card {
				background: #f8f9fa;
				padding: 1.5em;
				border-radius: 10px;
				text-align: center;
				box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
				transition: transform 0.2s;
			}
			
			.card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-5px);
			}
			
			.card h3 {
				color: #667eea;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
				font-size: 1.3em;
			}
			
			.cta {
				text-align: center;
				background: #667eea;
				color: white;
				padding: 2em;
				border-radius: 10px;
				font-size: 1.2em;
			}
			
			.cta a {
				color: #fff;
				text-decoration: underline;
				font-weight: bold;
			}
			
			main {
				padding: 1em;
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.hero h1 {
					font-size: 2em;
				}
				
				.tagline {
					font-size: 1.1em;
				}
				
				.grid {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
